reviewText: Please understand that the DVD itself is great. We bought this DVD though thinking it was going to be mainly about Minnie, but it wasn't. Only 1 episode was the Minnie Bowtique and the rest were other Mickey Mouse Clubhouse episodes. My son still enjoys the DVD, but if you are buying it strictly for Minnie them this may not be the DVD for you.
Title: Disney Mickey Mouse Clubhouse: Minnie's Bow-tique

reviewText: I bought this for my two granddaughters, 3 yrs and 20 months.  They adore it and watch again and again.
Title: Disney Mickey Mouse Clubhouse: Minnie's Bow-tique

reviewText: Ever since we bought this, my daughter (2yr old) will ask for "mouse on" at least once a day.  There are about 5-6 episodes on the disc and she has now gotten to the point that she can talk/sing along to parts of each episode.  Great entertainment for her and she's learning so much.  When I can't stand watching or listening, I can leave the room and she is still enthralled.  It was definitely worth it!!
Title: Disney Mickey Mouse Clubhouse: Minnie's Bow-tique
